{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"19020699c9","title":"关于时局正在变化中张、杨不会久处孤立致周恩来电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e9f1105139","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":23,"articleId":"19020699c9"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7aabff6bb0","type":"paragraph","text":"关于时局正在变化中张、杨不会久处孤立致周恩来电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"19020699c9"},{"id":"9cd8146fa5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月23日）周：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"19020699c9"},{"id":"a5f7829dd9","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、南汉臣（宸）来电，王世英去沪返南京即动身，他问回陕做何事。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"19020699c9"},{"id":"4bed9db667","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、津电二十九军高级干部开会，主张停止内战，开国民代表大会，解决国事，已授意教育界出面要求宋哲元发表此主张","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"19020699c9"},{"id":"f8ab2705d4","type":"paragraph","text":"内、时间正在变化中，张、杨不会久处孤立，但应告诉张、核及其干部，把工作放在困难点上，即使困难，奋斗到底，最后胜利是我们的。如无此种决心，则遇有挫折将不能支持，凡事向好坏两面着想，力争好的前途，同时也准备对付坏的局面。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"19020699c9"},{"id":"3afffc5b15","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东二十三日二十时","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"19020699c9"}],"page":{"id":"265cab4cc3","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"19020699c9","start":211,"end":211}}}},"__N_SSG":true}